metadata.name: AlfaCatalyst ~ VIP #100
metadata.description:
This is 1/1 out of 100 unique NFTs of this collection.

The NFT holder gets: 
 ⁃ exclusive access to the private AlfaCatalyst’s investors community on Telegram;
 ⁃ guaranteed opportunity to invest in some of the best early-stage crypto projects.

Allocations in projects will be primarily given to the private community. Each NFT holder is assured to get a project allocation.

Check out all the necessary information about the fund’s portfolio, as well as partners, on the following website - AlfaCatalyst.com

The access to the investment community remains valid as long as the investor holds the NFT in his/her own possession.

The investor might hand over his/her rights as an AflaCatalyst’s private investor to another person by transferring or reselling the NFT.

After buying NFT, send your wallet address which a purchase was made from to us at the following link: https://t.me/AlfaCatalyst_VIP

Our team will send you an individual invitation URL to the VIP community of investors.
